## Description {#details}

Base class for <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/denseset">DenseSet</a> and DenseSmallSet.

MapTy should be either

<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/densemap">DenseMap</a>&lt;ValueT, <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/detail/densesetempty">detail::DenseSetEmpty</a>, ValueInfoT, <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/detail/densesetpair">detail::DenseSetPair&lt;ValueT&gt;</a>&gt;

or the equivalent <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/smalldensemap">SmallDenseMap</a> type. ValueInfoT must implement the <a href="/docs/api/structs/llvm/densemapinfo">DenseMapInfo</a> &quot;concept&quot;.

Definition at line 54 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/adt/denseset-h">DenseSet.h</a>.
